# ABOUT HELIX

Tips! :
- selection word just use 'b.e' 'e.b' than 'm.i.w'
- selection to last line use t<Return> than use 'v.g.l'

> ALL HELIX COMMANDS
	- w : write
	- q : quit
	- e : edit/add (file)
	- o : open (file)
	- pwd : view directory
	- cd : change directory
	- mv : move
	- theme : change theme.
	- config-open : open configuration.
	- bc : close buffer
	- bn : buffer next
	- bn : buffer prev
	- hs,vs : split (horizontal, vertical) 'q' for quit
	- sh : cmd
	- pipe : open pipe mode
	- sort : automatic sort number, -r for reverse direction
	- reflow $num : reflow line/paragraf
	- read <file.> : paste entire file in the current buffer
	- 

> ALL HELIX SHORTCUTS
	- g : Goto mode options !important
	- m : Match mode options !important
	- ctrl + w : window mode options !important
	- z : view mode options !important
	- " : open register mode
	- [, ] : Bracket mode
	
	- hjkl : move cursor
	- Space + b : Ganti buffer (tab switcher)
	- ctrl  + c : add comments
	- $num  + j : Lompat ke bawah $num baris
	- $num  + k : Lompat ke atas $num baris
	- w, e : next
	- b : back
	- f,F : find huruf in line (next, before).
	- i,a,o : insert(before,after,newline)
	- ctrl + d,u : (up, down) cursor
	- ctrl + f,b : (forward, back) page
	- $num + G(g+g) : jump to line $num
	- ctrl + i,o : (in, out) from file using [g+f]
	- v : visual mode.
	- d : delete/cut
	- x : select line.
	- p : paste
	- y : yank(copyr)
	- r : replace
	- c : change
	- u,U : undo, redo
	- / : search (use 'n' to next, 'N' to prev)
	- * : cari kalimat yang di select
	- . : duplicate tulisan terakhir
	- J : joining line
	- m + i + p : select paragraph
	- >, < : space tab (intend, unintended)
	- m + m : jump antara bracket
	- gp, gn : go to (prev, next) buffer.
	- ctrl + a,x : (increment,Decrement) the number
	- (alt +) C : Multiple Cursor, press ',' to exit
	- (alt +) , : cancel multiple cursor one by one
	- % : select all
	- s : select mode (select dalam selection)
	- & : merapihkan antarbaris (multicursor mode)
	- alt + s : ubah multiple select menjadi multi cursor
	- space + j : open jumplist picker
	- space + d,D : open diasnostic mode
	- ~ : Mengubah huruf UPPERCASE <-> lowercase
	- Space + r : Rename Symbol
	- Q : Macro mode (recording action) press 'Q' to save
	- q : Replay macro action (macro bisa di save di register mode " )
	- ! : insert command (cmd) and type in the editor
	- | : pipe each slection to the shell command
	- ctrl + r + # : make list indeks in multi cursor mode

	GOTO:
	|Shortcut|Fungsi|
	|--------|------|
	|g.d|ke isi kode asli|
	|g.D|ke deklarasi simbol|
	|g.y|ke tipe definisi|
	|g.r|lihat kesemua pemakaian (list)|
	|g.i|ke implementasi konkret|

	- g + d : Goto {definition} symbol,
		kalo mau lihat isi kode didalam fungsi yang dipanggil ( 'greet()' ).
		Contoh : ```js
			function greet(name) { // lompat ke greet() ini
				return `Hello ${name}`
			}
			greet("Salman"); // tekan shortcutnya disini!
		```;
		
	- g + D : Goto {Declaration}
		Sama seperti Goto definition cuman:
		- Definition: "di mana ini diperkenalkan?".
		- Declaration: "di mana ini diisi/dideclarasikan?"
		Contoh:```greet.d.ts
			export declare function greet(name: string): string; // lompat ke sini
		```;
		```main.ts
			greet("Salman"); // tekan shorcut disini!
		```;

	- g + y : Goto type {definition}
		Contoh : ```ts
			type User = { // lompat ke sini
				id: number;
				name: string;
			};

			const u: User = { id: 1, name: "Salman" }; // tekan shortcut di sini!
		```;

	- g + r : Goto {References}
		- membuka list semua yang berkaitan dengan symbol
		Contoh : ```
			function sum(a, b){
				return a + b;
			}
			sum(1, 2); // tekan shortcut disalah satu sum() maka akan membuka list semua 'sum()' berada.
			sum(2, 4);
		```;
		
	- g + i : Goto Implementation
		- Lompat ke impementasi konkret dari interface/trait/abstract (paling terasa di TYpescript, java, Rust, Go)
		- untuk mencari class yang mengimplementasikan interface (console.log)
		- jika lebih dari satu, ditampilkan list
		Contoh : ```
			interface Animal { // tekan shortcut di sini!
			  speak(): void;
			}
			
			class Dog implements Animal { // lompat ke sini
			  speak() {
			    console.log("Woof");
			  }
			}		
		```;
